<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 15:11:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>在罗马争执中，Stellantis 首席执行官表示意大利工厂有未来</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/amid-rome-spat-stellantis-ceo-says-italy-plants-have-future-2024-02-15/</link><description>Stellantis首席执行官卡洛斯·塔瓦雷斯(Carlos Tavares)周四表示，该汽车制造商将需要其所有意大利工厂来实现其在那里的长期生产目标，这一和解言论可能会缓解菲亚特汽车制造商与罗马之间的紧张关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 13:28:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/amid-rome-spat-stellantis-ceo-says-italy-plants-have-future-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>Joo的梅开二度帮助蔚山进入亚洲冠军联赛四分之一决赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/joos-brace-moves-ulsan-verge-asian-champions-league-quarters-2024-02-15/</link><description>周四，蔚山现代队在蔚山文殊体育场以 3-0 击败日本乙级联赛甲府文特林队，踏入亚洲冠军联赛四分之一决赛。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 12:15:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/joos-brace-moves-ulsan-verge-asian-champions-league-quarters-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>数百万人从农历新年旅行归来，预计中国将迎来寒流</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/cold-snap-expected-china-millions-return-lunar-new-year-trips-2024-02-15/</link><description>国家气象台周四表示，预计从本周末开始，一股寒流将席卷中国大部分地区，随着数百万人春节旅行归来，气温将下降高达20摄氏度。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 11:56:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/cold-snap-expected-china-millions-return-lunar-new-year-trips-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：强调科技主导的美国“例外主义”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-graphics-2024-02-15/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 11:02:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-graphics-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>马克龙和泽连斯基将于周五签署双边安全协议 - 爱丽舍宫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/macron-zelenskiy-sign-bilateral-security-agreement-friday-elysee-2024-02-15/</link><description>法国总统周四表示，法国和乌克兰将于本周五签署一项关于安全承诺的双边协议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 09:38:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/macron-zelenskiy-sign-bilateral-security-agreement-friday-elysee-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>葛兰素史克 (GSK) 以高达 14 亿美元完成对 Aiolos Bio 的收购</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/gsk-completes-acquisition-aiolos-bio-up-14-bln-2024-02-15/</link><description>葛兰素史克周四表示，已完成对 Aiolos Bio 的收购，Aiolos Bio 是一家专注于呼吸和炎症疾病的临床阶段生物制药公司。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 07:41:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/gsk-completes-acquisition-aiolos-bio-up-14-bln-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>独家：俄罗斯人利用中国合作伙伴在闲置的斯特兰蒂斯工厂生产雪铁龙汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/russians-use-chinese-partner-produce-citroen-cars-idled-stellantis-plant-2024-02-15/</link><description>汽车制造商 Stellantis 于 2022 年 4 月停止在俄罗斯的生产。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 06:33:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/russians-use-chinese-partner-produce-citroen-cars-idled-stellantis-plant-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>保乐力加股价因增长复苏的希望而上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/pernod-ricard-vise-un-ca-globalement-stable-pour-son-exercice-202324-2024-02-15/</link><description>法国烈酒制造商保乐力加 (Pernod Ricard) 的股价周四上涨超过 6%，尽管该公司下调了全年销售预期和股票回购计划，但仍保持其长期增长目标不变。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 06:24:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/pernod-ricard-vise-un-ca-globalement-stable-pour-son-exercice-202324-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>上次阿波罗登月任务半个世纪后，美国私人月球着陆器发射升空</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/private-us-moon-lander-launched-half-century-after-last-apollo-lunar-mission-2024-02-15/</link><description>周四早些时候，总部位于休斯敦的航空航天公司 Intuitive Machines 制造的月球着陆器从佛罗里达州发射升空，其任务是进行美国半个多世纪以来的首次月球着陆，也是私人航天器的首次着陆。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 06:10:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/private-us-moon-lander-launched-half-century-after-last-apollo-lunar-mission-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾承诺遵守南海行为准则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-committed-south-china-sea-code-conduct-2024-02-15/</link><description>菲律宾外长周四表示，菲律宾坚定致力于中国与东南亚国家之间就行为准则进行谈判，以避免南海对抗。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 05:47:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-committed-south-china-sea-code-conduct-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国抱怨前线岛屿附近发生致命事故后，台湾捍卫海岸警卫队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-defends-coast-guard-after-china-complains-over-fatal-accident-near-2024-02-15/</link><description>周四，台湾为其海岸警卫队的行动进行了辩护，此前一艘中国快艇因太靠近台湾前线岛屿而在试图逃离海岸警卫队船只时翻船，造成两人死亡。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 05:34:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-defends-coast-guard-after-china-complains-over-fatal-accident-near-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>随着经济放缓，一些中国年轻人放弃了企业工作，转而追求“自我时间”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/some-chinese-youth-spurn-corporate-jobs-me-time-economy-slows-2024-02-15/</link><description>面对经济放缓带来的就业前景黯淡，褚毅选择“平躺”，这是一个中文术语，用来形容那些工作只够花时间做自己喜欢的事情的人。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 01:09:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/some-chinese-youth-spurn-corporate-jobs-me-time-economy-slows-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>部分大众汽车因中国零件在美国港口延误</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/some-volkswagen-cars-delayed-us-ports-over-chinese-part-2024-02-14/</link><description>大众汽车周三表示，预计将在 3 月底之前解决因海关问题而滞留在美国港口的数千辆汽车的交付延误问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 20:54:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/some-volkswagen-cars-delayed-us-ports-over-chinese-part-2024-02-14/</guid></item><item><title>独家：德国对华投资创历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/german-investment-china-rises-new-record-high-2024-02-14/</link><description>IW研究所分析的德国央行官方数据显示，去年德国对华直接投资增长4.3%，达到创纪录的119亿欧元（127亿美元），占德国对外投资总额的比重也有所增加。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 09:16:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/german-investment-china-rises-new-record-high-2024-02-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国、美国主导的全球补充枯竭石油库存有望提振需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-us-led-global-refill-depleted-oil-stocks-seen-buoying-demand-2024-02-14/</link><description>分析师和交易商表示，随着中东紧张局势威胁到主要航道，推动补充耗尽的石油库存（尤其是在中国、美国和欧洲）可能会在未来几个月提振需求和价格。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 07:09:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-us-led-global-refill-depleted-oil-stocks-seen-buoying-demand-2024-02-14/</guid></item></channel></rss>